description:
Childhood is awesome and we believe in documenting it authentically. Keep the best photos, videos, quotes, and more about your kids in one safe place. Share with those who care most using the Notabli app, the web, or through timely emails (no iPhone or iPad needed for viewers).

• Ad-free
• Retain ownership of the content you post.
• Save photos, quotes, videos, audio, and notes about your kids. 
• Optionally mark moments as Private, so they are only visible to you and other parent.
• Export your kids moments at any time.
• Choose photos & videos directly from Instagram.
• Selectively share moments to Facebook, Tumblr, and Twitter.
• Also keep up the kids you care about.

We're happy to help you get started or along the way: hello@notabli.com
